latestIgtvVideos.title: Happy 3rd Birthday our Storie Bear🐻💙
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Our amazing beautiful Son, the boy that made us Mummy & Daddy, and lit up our life. You will never understand how much we love you, but we will tell you every single day so you do. Anyone who knows you, knows how special you are. You my side kick, my little helper, my shopping partner, my favourite person to go to Starbucks with, the funniest boy ever, but the most loving and caring gentle boy we could of ever imagined, whose become the best big brother to Bowie. We are so proud of you and thank our lucky stars every single day that you are ours. Let’s eat sweets and chocolate all day and fill our house with even more cars 😅😂🤍🤍🤍🤍

latestIgtvVideos.title: My Beachy/Curly Wave 🌊 tutorial
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This is how I create my more holiday beachy wave tutorial glam hair! Not as many Ums this time guys as a good friend of mine @sam_theglambox told me the trick is to speak to the camera like it’s your friend so I took that on board Sam 🥰😋
I have 4 packs of @spectrumonehairextensions in my hair. 
I used the @bombayhair 25mm rose gold cutler which is amazing! #gifted 
And I use tresamme volume moose on wet hair and furterer Paris vegetal texture spray which is amazing for all hair styles! Have a fab week 🥰❤️

latestIgtvVideos.title: How I Do My Hair 💞
latestIgtvVideos.caption: I’m totally new to this and soooo out my comfort zone hence the fact I say umm about a thousand times.. but here goes with the best hair extensions ever a quick overview of how I style my hair I use straighteners on my extensions and a hairdryer on my top and then set them in rollers leave them for about 1-2 hours and then brush them out and back comb the roots of my hair at the top and spray with volume spray to keep them all nice and volumised I find this is the best way for me and my tape extensions to keep the curl in longer!  @spectrumonehairextensions @spectrum_showcase

latestIgtvVideos.title: My baby turns❤️2️⃣❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption: 2 Years Ago today at 1.23pm 05.03.18 Our Lives Changed Forever When our boy was born. How was there a life without you! We Never knew love could run so deep until We had you Storie Bear. You have grown into the sweetest, kindest, gentlest, cuddly little boy who has me laughing constantly! You’ve been stuck by my hip for 2 years baby and we have forever for it to stay that way. You’ll never know how much mummy and daddy love you but we will make sure to tell you every single day! We love you so much baby boy 💙 let’s play all day long!!
